'''Akarere ka Huye''' ni kamwe mu Turere umunani tugize [[Intara y'amajyepfo|Intara y’Amajyepfo]] mu [[Rwanda]].

Iyi gahunda yateguwe hashingiye ku bibazo byihariye bigaragara mu Karere ka Huye. Ibindi byashingiweho mu gutegura iyi mihigo ni Imihigo y’Umuryango n’Umudugudu, iy’Utugari n’Imirenge. 

Akarere ka Huye kazwi na none kuba gafite inzu ndangamuco y'u Rwanda.
Ni mu karere ka Huye kandi dusanga amahoteri menshi mu gace kahoze kitwa Butare.

